01:12:01,184 --> 01:12:03,228
Ya.

885
01:12:03,395 --> 01:12:06,189
Aku rasa begitu.

886
01:12:21,660 --> 01:12:23,829
Lihat... Itu dia.

887
01:12:25,414 --> 01:12:27,541
Astaga. Warna darahnya salah!

888
01:12:27,707 --> 01:12:30,210
Kenapa mereka melakukan
